c Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is AI Scribe in healthcare?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI Scribe is an AI-powered documentation tool that records and transcribes patient encounters, then generates structured clinical notes such as SOAP Notes, Visit Summaries, or Referral Letters. It helps providers save time, reduce errors, and focus more on patient care."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does AI Scribe improve provider productivity?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Instead of typing or dictating notes, providers can conduct natural conversations with patients while AI Scribe captures key details and stores them in an Encounter Log which is a critical record of the encounter. Providers can also add their own notes to the Encounter Log. The AI Scribe then generates Consultation Documents based on the context available in the Encounter Log and in the patient's health record and drafts a structured Consultation Document based on the document template that the provider needs e.g. SOAP Note or Patient Visit Summary etc. The provider should then edit this AI Scribe generated draft document. This reduces after-hours paperwork and improves consistency."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What kinds of documents can AI Scribe generate?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI Scribe can generate SOAP Notes, H&P Notes, Patient Visit Summaries, Referral Letters, and Medical Certificates. Providers can also build custom templates with AI assistance to meet specialty-specific or organizational needs."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does AI Scribe integrate with the EHR?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. AI Scribe integrates with the Virtual Practice EHR. Generated documents will be stored in the patient's record and shared with patients securely via their portal or app. Visibility of documents to patients can be controlled."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can multiple providers or teams use AI Scribe templates?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The Virtual Practice supports a set of default AI Document templates. Additionally Providers can create their own templates and optionally share them as Team Templates, ensuring consistent documentation standards across a clinic or multi-provider startup."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is AI Scribe HIPAA and GDPR compliant?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. AI Scribe runs on HIPAA-compliant systems with end-to-end encryption, role-based access, audit trails, and strict data retention policies. Audio recordings are deleted per defined schedules."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Who controls patient data when using AI Scribe?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You remain the Data Controller. ContinuousCare only processes and stores patient data on your behalf while your subscription is active. Data is never repurposed or shared, and you can export records if you leave the platform."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does AI Scribe replace clinical judgment?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. AI Scribe supports providers by drafting documentation and organizing reasoning, but final review and edits always rest with the provider. Clinical decisions remain the sole responsibility of the healthcare professional."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How accurate are AI-generated notes and transcriptions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The AI Scribe can recognize medical terminology and reasoning with high accuracy. However, providers must review and finalize documents to ensure clinical correctness and completeness."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What types of healthcare providers benefit most from AI Scribe?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Any provider who documents patient encounters—whether in primary care, mental health, chronic care, or specialty practice—can benefit. It's especially valuable for high-volume clinics, telehealth services, and startups needing efficiency."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What is AI Scribe in healthcare?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What is AI Scribe in healthcare?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="How does AI Scribe improve provider productivity?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">How does AI Scribe improve provider productivity?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What kinds of documents can AI Scribe generate?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What kinds of documents can AI Scribe generate?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Does AI Scribe integrate with the EHR?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">Does AI Scribe integrate with the EHR?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div 